list.comment: Fabrik tags no longer display the label if the value is null (this resolves '--- Please Select ---' appearing in emails).

task.summary: Fixed a bug causing evaluations to not display for Coordinators who have multiple profiles. Fixed another bug which broke the Evaluation elements list in the XLS export dialog.
Added the message HTML structure to emails sent by triggers.
Fabrik tags no longer display the label if the value is null (this resolves '--- Please Select ---' appearing in emails).
Added a new plugin which replaces the old campaign plugin but can now have a custom redirect URL. Added a custom Fabrik form layout for a specific form. Fixed some ugly code.
